<br>
And it all can be blamed on that damn Clan McMarrin.<br>
<br>
After giving her heart's life and blood to the Wolves of the North for countless seasons and even more countless battles, she returned home, to Halas, in order to rest. With her then-husband at her side, she set about living what she considered to be a &quot;normal&quot; life. Taking care of house and home, as well as their newborn daughter Severina, she settled into the role of wife and mother.<br>
<br>
Then everything came crashing down.<br>
<br>
Her husband was charged of trying to smuggle contraband into Halas from Qeynos, convicted, and executed in the barest mockeries of a trial. Never mind the fact that there was proof he not only never left Halas, but had nothing to do with it! Xarien herself avoided the same fate when she proved that while she had not been active in the life of an adventurer, she was still a damn sight better with the sword! Having won her challenge, Clan McMarrin whined like the dogs they are to the Clan Council, claiming that her victory was invalid, seeing as her equipment was obviously superior to theirs.<br>
<br>
She watched in horror as the Clan Council, unwilling to lose the support of the McMarrins, sided with them against her. However, Clan Felligan proposed that, rather than execute her, to exile her to the frozen tundra of Everfrost. A punishment Xarien sadly accepted.<br>
<br>
After being escorted to her home to pack their belongings, and then to the pier leading from Halas, she addressed the four people that served as escorts. To Walthor Felligan, she gave thanks, and promised not to forget what he did. To Hetie McDonald, she thanked for the extra supplies. To Kylan O`Danos, she thanked for being her trainer for so many years.<br>
<br>
However, to Andres McMarrin, she spat in his face and vowed the Vengeance of the Warlord upon him, and that justice truly would prevail, upon him and his arrogant Clan. She then stepped onto the platform and left Halas.<br>
<br>
That was fifteen years ago. <p><font color="red"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46795" target="_blank">Xarien Somberstar</a><BR>
