<br>
However, it didn't look like she could run anywhere this time, a fact further reinforced by the iron bars that were the door.<br>
<br>
Slowly assuming a sitting position, her first thought was how to get rid of the massive headache she had. However, the sound of metallic footsteps quickly brought that to a close, especially when she realized that her weapon and her spellbook were missing.<br>
<br>
The door opened, and two Teir`Dal guards entered, wearing full plate armor and carrying their weapons in hand. A third person approached, wearing the garments of a priest. What the priest said shocked and chilled her to the bone:<br>
<br>
&quot;Your father wishes to speak to you.&quot; <p><font color="red"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46795" target="_blank">Xarien Somberstar</a><BR>
